    "description": "Yamato Mobility & Mfg. Co.,Ltd. primarily engages in the planning, design, manufacturing, and sale of injection molding products in Japan and internationally. The company offers automation equipment parts, SP products, logistics equipment, home appliances and medical equipment, housing equipment, automotive parts, household goods, information communication related products, nursing care products, etc. It also manufactures and sells various synthetic resin molded products; and provides vacuum, press, and RTM molding products. In addition, the company offers vacuum forming/vacuum forming, signs and billboards, and fixtures and other items. The company was formerly known as Yamato Industry Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Yamato Mobility & Mfg. Co.,Ltd. in October 2024. Yamato Mobility & Mfg. Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1937 and is headquartered in Kawagoe, Japan."
